actions.message:
**All User Commands:**
```
!help                          Displays this nice Help message!
!number (minimum) (maximum)    Generates a random # in between your choice!
!tacos                         Send Tacos!
!ip                            Sends our IP so you can join us on MC!
```

**Per Permission Commands:**
```
!clear  (# of messages to del) Deletes X amount of messages you set
```

actions.message: **${tempVars("randomnumber")}** is your random number between `${tempVars("start")}` and `${tempVars("end")}`
